Author: Cute-dead
Text: I know how that feels :( sometimes the things going on on the inside doesn't reflect what's going on on the outside

Author: audreyhepburnwho
Text: I go through these periods ss well. Not long ago i was deep in a long binge cycle and my work was piling on, i looked a mess every, my apartment was chaotic and i wasn't replying to anyone's messages or calls. Now I'm deep into restricting again. I'm collecting overtime because I'm so pumped to get everything done at work, I'm cooking and cleaning almost daily, meal prepping healthy stuff, my cat gets more attention, ny friends get more attention, my apartment looks nice  and clean and I'm taking better care of myself. Except I'm very much under eating and overexercising. I definitely like this version better though. I wish it weren't that way but i do.
